{"tid":1272540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"41名建制派議員嚴厲譴責有極端激進份子破壞立會大樓","createTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T12:56:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":281,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1e616055413e7028ccd0c82191c5d401c3d3f46d","tid":1272540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"立法會大樓今日受示威者嚴重衝擊，有41名建制派立法會議員發表聯合聲明，嚴厲譴責極端激進暴力份子的惡行。<br />\n<br />\n聯合聲明說，今日再有極端激進暴力份子，發動連串違法行動，不單堵塞和佔領幹道、更將立法會廣場的國旗，換上黑色洋紫荊圖案的旗，甚至有人將帶有腐蝕性的液體潑向警方，做成10多名警員受傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">有途人就被毆打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他們持續多個小時用大型手推車和硬物衝擊立法會大樓，令大樓受到嚴重破壞。<br />\n<br />\n建制派批評，極端激進暴力份子存心搞事，擾亂公眾秩序，挑戰法治，嚴厲譴責他們的暴行，並呼籲愛好和平、堅信香港核心價值的市民，與他們劃清界線，向他們發出不容破壞社會秩序的訊息。<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派亦呼籲民主派議員要分清黑白，譴責這些暴力份子，維護法治。</span> 聲明表示，支持警方依法執法，追究違法份子，將他們繩之於法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466043-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466043-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=7eca91bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466043-20190701.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=361558bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466043-20190701.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n想分化?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d221e904dc90bf6571cb4c2b65fc4d509f6e8a03","tid":1272540,"uid":34515,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3位義士</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">轉：立會需要水、頭盔、索帶、遮、first aid、較剪、眼罩、盾牌、紙皮、六角匙、頭盔、較剪<br />\n物資短缺！